author: Rebecca Burn-Callander
title: Buyers circle Jimmy's Iced Coffee as turnover tops £2m
text: Buyers circle Jimmy's Iced Coffee as turnover tops £2m The start-up has bounced back from its manufacturing nightmares this summer to secure a further supermarket listing Brother and sister duo Suzie and Jimmy Cregan set up Jimmy's Iced Coffee in 2010 By Rebecca Burn-Callander , Enterprise Editor 7:40PM BST 05 Oct 2015
